5️⃣ Seat Locking System (Redis)

Major problem in ticket systems:

Two users selecting same seat

Solution:

Redis atomic seat locking

Implementation:

Redis SET NX EX

Example key:

show:123:seat:A1

Flow:

User selects seat
      ↓
Seat locked in Redis
      ↓
Lock expires after 5 minutes

Benefits:

Prevents double booking
High speed locking
Auto expiry
