7️⃣ Payment Integration (Razorpay)

Payment flow:

User clicks pay
      ↓
Backend creates Razorpay order
      ↓
User completes payment
      ↓
Razorpay sends webhook
      ↓
Backend verifies webhook
      ↓
Booking confirmed

Webhook verification:

HMAC SHA256 signature validation

Important security step:

Idempotency check

Prevents:

Duplicate webhook processing
8️⃣ QR Ticket System

After successful payment:

JWT token generated

Token contains:

bookingId
showId
seats

Then converted into QR code:

QRCode.toDataURL()

Stored in booking.

Purpose:

Secure ticket verification
9️⃣ Ticket Scanning System

At theatre entry:

Flow:

Staff scans QR code
      ↓
Frontend sends token
      ↓
Backend verifies JWT
      ↓
Booking validated
      ↓
Entry allowed

Extra check:

ticketUsed flag

Prevents ticket reuse.

🔟 Real Time Seat Updates (Socket.IO)

Implemented using Socket.IO.

When a seat is locked:

Backend emits event

Example:

seatLocked
seatBooked
seatUnlocked

Frontend receives event and updates seat UI instantly.

Benefits:

Real time seat availability
Better user experience
No API polling
1️⃣1️⃣ Booking Expiry (Cron Job)

If payment not completed:

Booking expires automatically

Implemented using:

node-cron

Process:

Find expired bookings
Release Redis locks
Mark booking as expired

This frees seats for other users.

